snippet.title: Valkyria Chronicles 2 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Band together to save Gallia once more! Lead your fellow cadets through a heroic journey as Gallia erupts into civil war against the Rebel Army.

Out now in Europe only on Sony Playstation Portable. Rated PEGI 16.
